## Fix Strategy

### Phase 1: Fix seed_demo.py (Bugs 2-6) — 30 min
Patch ALL namespaces with realistic demo data so the CAM report looks professional:
- `pan_intelligence`: verified PAN, full name, status ACTIVE
- `mca_intelligence`: company ACTIVE, director info, no defaults
- `financials`: proper revenue in lakhs, real DSCR/ICR values
- `stress_results`: realistic DSCR values (1.2-1.8 range)
- `decision_confidence`: confidence 0.78, proper formula

### Phase 2: Fix VectorAI search (Bug 1) — 30 min
Rewrite `seed_vectorai.py` to use the official `actian_vectorai` SDK:
- Create all 14 collections with `VectorParams(size=384, distance=Distance.Cosine)`
- Embed and insert 41 sample documents
- Update backend `/api/vectorai/search` endpoint to use the gRPC client

### Phase 3: Fix Pipeline & UI (Bugs 7-9) — 20 min
- Show realistic VectorAI traffic stats
- Fix Monitor/PAN agent status display
- Fix Recent Activity text mapping
